    "title": "scriptpubkeyman fuzz target TopUp is slow",
    "body": "Seems wasteful to spend time in `TopUp` while fuzzing, so my recommendation would be to limit TopUp iterations a bit.\r\n\r\nContext: https://cirrus-ci.com/task/6178647134961664?logs=ci#L4357\r\n\r\n```\r\nRun scriptpubkeyman with args ['/ci_container_base/ci/scratch/build/bitcoin-x86_64-pc-linux-gnu/src/test/fuzz/fuzz', '-runs=1', PosixPath('/ci_container_base/ci/scratch/qa-assets/fuzz_seed_corpus/scriptpubkeyman')]INFO: Running with entropic power schedule (0xFF, 100).\r\nINFO: Seed: 3840853548\r\nINFO: Loaded 1 modules   (623498 inline 8-bit counters): 623498 [0x5572c2e0a518, 0x5572c2ea28a2), \r\nINFO: Loaded 1 PC tables (623498 PCs): 623498 [0x5572c2ea28a8,0x5572c3826148), \r\nINFO:     8841 files found in /ci_container_base/ci/scratch/qa-assets/fuzz_seed_corpus/scriptpubkeyman\r\nINFO: -max_len is not provided; libFuzzer will not generate inputs larger than 924704 bytes\r\nINFO: seed corpus: files: 8841 min: 1b max: 924704b total: 49718183b rss: 173Mb\r\n#128\tpulse  cov: 12139 ft: 24855 corp: 125/930b exec/s: 25 rss: 191Mb\r\n#256\tpulse  cov: 15522 ft: 49362 corp: 251/2416b exec/s: 4 rss: 286Mb\r\n#512\tpulse  cov: 19356 ft: 64381 corp: 483/6374b exec/s: 3 rss: 448Mb\r\nSlowest unit: 18 s:\r\nartifact_prefix='./'; Test unit written to ./slow-unit-c9b8928cecb1edc192fb2d5816b4b7878cdfcf50\r\nBase64: dHIoJTI5LzMvKicpXCUprSlUVO3t/e3t7e3tra2t7e0=\r\n#1024\tpulse  cov: 21215 ft: 88717 corp: 877/17Kb exec/s: 2 rss: 610Mb\r\n#2048\tpulse  cov: 21835 ft: 104559 corp: 1467/57Kb exec/s: 2 rss: 653Mb\r\n#4096\tpulse  cov: 23163 ft: 120057 corp: 2005/171Kb exec/s: 2 rss: 694Mb\r\n#8192\tpulse  cov: 24591 ft: 135480 corp: 2490/1045Kb exec/s: 3 rss: 849Mb\r\n#8844\tINITED cov: 24681 ft: 137958 corp: 2568/7024Kb exec/s: 3 rss: 1001Mb\r\n#8844\tDONE   cov: 24681 ft: 137958 corp: 2568/7024Kb lim: 793168 exec/s: 3 rss: 1001Mb\r\nDone 8844 runs in 2763 second(s)\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n```\r\n$ FUZZ=scriptpubkeyman perf record -g --call-graph dwarf  ./src/test/fuzz/fuzz -